    <h2 class="section-heading">About</h2>
    <p>
      I'm a mobile engineer. For six years I was the only frontend developer
      on Guusto's React Native app: I built it from scratch and shipped it to
      both stores. My work covers the whole pipeline — Figma handoff,
      TypeScript, native integrations, client-side push, and the
      release-engineering grind nobody notices until it breaks: cert renewals,
      store review rejections, crash triage. Based in Japan on a spouse visa
      (no sponsorship needed), native English speaker, learning Japanese. I
      worked fully remote the whole six years, from Canada, then Australia,
      then Japan. Same Vancouver team the entire time, across gaps as wide as
      16 hours. Mostly that meant a good handoff note before bed and reading
      Slack before coffee.
    </p>
